---
title: Big Island Pork Burgers with Pineapple plus Tangy Slaw and Spicy Mayo
description: If you love pork and pineapple, this is your burger! You’ll tuck juicy pork patties into fluffy brioche buns spread with spicy mayo, and top with juicy pineapple. Serve with a creamy, tangy cabbage and carrot slaw tossed with cilantro and lime juice for a bright hit of fresh flavor and crunchiness, and prepare for island vibes all around.
